00:34:41,621 --> 00:34:44,206
Meanwhile, my dad's freaked out

767
00:34:44,207 --> 00:34:47,543
because on his floor
the nurses are male.

768
00:34:47,544 --> 00:34:51,171
In his mind,
good nurses are female, period.

